The creative industries are almost the first to encounter deep complexity because they are often creating a product that has never been created before or attempting to solve a problem that has never been solved before.

It is also very difficult to make knowledge work visible and transparent, but #kanban makes short work of that. In this short video, Martin Hinshelwood talks about the reasons behind the rise of #kanban in creative industries.

